{"tid":2150543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係好有愛","createTime":"2020-08-11T03:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T06:17:24.000Z","uid":304619,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"127f7e2bd51c234ace9ea4a97a9b0e61bbfc339f","tid":2150543,"uid":304619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tEja0Vo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtEja0Vo.png&h=480d6762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撐蘋果日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法生效逾月，政權終向新聞自由開刀！警方國安處連同刑事處人員昨晨展開大規模拘捕行動，以違反港版國安法等罪名，拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、他兩名兒子、四名壹傳媒高層及前香港眾志成員周庭等共10人。逾200警員更有恃無恐直闖蘋果日報大樓，翻天覆地搜查近九小時，其間更肆無忌憚在編採部翻閱記者新聞採訪資料。本報一如昨日許諾，今天如常出版，黎智英昨在被捕時直言：「煮到嚟咪食。」壹傳媒行政總裁、《蘋果日報》社長張劍虹就表示：「蘋果一定可以撐落去！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDt76Yens3O/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDt76Yens3O%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=0a933e5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDt76Yens3O%2F&h=11b001dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CDt76Yens3O/</a>"},{"pid":"506ea2b8353d36b49dd23272b2d38c24ee2c1b8e","tid":2150543,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b2a9d640733a1f14313ccc65d9a1eebf0a5bc1","tid":2150543,"uid":304619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"506ea2b8353d36b49dd23272b2d38c24ee2c1b8e","tid":2150543,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\"